title: Really beautiful scenery from the windows of this 3 bed
posting_body: Situated in Georgetown, a quaint northern suburb of Austin, it's the perfect blend of city living and small-town charm.
You’ll love this beautiful three bedroom apartment with stunning Hill Country views, not to mention the designer interior features and exceptional amenities.
And the convenient location near Southwestern University, Wolf Ranch Shopping Center, and Georgetown Square means you’re close to fabulous shopping, scrumptious dining, and buzzing entertainment.
With close proximity to TX 130, you're a quick drive south to Austin or north toward Ft. Hood.
Your palace with panoramic views awaits!
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
